				<div style="font-style:italic">You've got to be kidding me. You don't think it was completely abusive for people to load up on +dmg gear, and use rank 1 spells to outdamage their peers who were using their current rank spells? This is an unfortunate strategy that was built up around a totally flawed premise that doesn't even make sense from a gaming or fantasy perspective. </div>
			
