So, is the problem the spell or itemization?<br />
 <br />
Clearly the use of rank one frostbolt without +dmg gear doesn't raise any flags here.  So when you make this comparison, you're making it between a geared and non geared player.  How is that different than melee itemization and relative levels of gear.<br />
 <br />
The itemization team probably should have more than token representation from the balance team.  It's not our imaginations that gear issues are increasingly breaking class balance.<br />
 <br />
This case seems a clear cut example of broken itemization implementation.</div>
